com.intuit.wasabi.analytics

Interface Analytics

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AnalyticsImpl

    public interface Analytics
    This interface specifies methods to compute statistics on an Experiment.

      • getExperimentRollup

        ExperimentCounts getExperimentRollup(Experiment.ID experimentId,
                                     Parameters parameters)
        Returns a number of summary counts for the specified experiment, using rollups if possible. First queries the rollup table to retrieve counts. If no valid rollups exist, calls getExperimentCounts(com.intuit.wasabi.experimentobjects.Experiment.ID, com.intuit.wasabi.analyticsobjects.Parameters) to do full queries for counts data.
        Parameters:
        experimentId - the unique Experiment.ID
        parameters - API parameters Parameters
        Returns:
        ExperimentCounts

      • getExperimentRollupDailies

        ExperimentCumulativeCounts getExperimentRollupDailies(Experiment.ID experimentId,
                                                      Parameters parameters)
        Returns a number of summary counts for the specified experiment, by day, using rollups if possible. First queries the rollup table to retrieve counts. If no valid rollups exist, calls getExperimentCountsDailies(com.intuit.wasabi.experimentobjects.Experiment.ID, com.intuit.wasabi.analyticsobjects.Parameters) to do full queries for counts data.
        Parameters:
        experimentId - the unique Experiment.ID
        parameters - API parameters Parameters
        Returns:
        ExperimentCumulativeCounts

      • getExperimentStatistics

        ExperimentStatistics getExperimentStatistics(Experiment.ID experimentId,
                                             Parameters parameters)
        Queries the datastore and returns a number of summary counts and statistics for the specified experiment. Statistics are calculated from unique counts.
        Parameters:
        experimentId - the unique experiment ID
        parameters - API parameters
        Returns:
        ExperimentStatistics

      • getExperimentStatisticsDailies

        ExperimentCumulativeStatistics getExperimentStatisticsDailies(Experiment.ID experimentId,
                                                              Parameters parameters)
        Queries the database and returns a number of summary counts and statistics for the specified experiment, by day. Statistics are calculated from unique counts and comparison statistics are only calculated for cumulative counts.
        Parameters:
        experimentId - experiment id
        parameters - parameters
        Returns:
        ExperimentCumulativeStatistics
